org.treetank.bucket

Class BucketFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.treetank.bucket.BucketFactory

  • public final class BucketFactory
extends Object
    Factory to deserialize buckets out of a chunk of bytes. This factory needs a INodeFactory-reference to perform inlying node-serializations as well.
    Author:
    Sebastian Graf, University of Konstanz
